{"tid":1389793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"亨利：放膽做，民意只係欺善怕惡","createTime":"2019-07-31T03:46:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T16:19:48.000Z","uid":29006,"like":59,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"da8e57e376fb33b5d0bbc17e50aaf54ce79eecac","tid":1389793,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:46:33.000Z","msg":"節錄亨利節目所講：<br />\n<br />\n民意只係欺善怕惡，佢舉咗個例子<br />\n<br />\n中學入面瘦弱男被三個強壯男打，正義男出面幫瘦弱男但不敵，最後仲激起怒火令三個強壯男打多瘦弱男幾拳。瘦弱男無感激正義男，仲怪責佢害佢比人打多幾拳。<br />\n<br />\n今日今日所謂「民意」其實都一樣，當各位義士爭取嘅嘢有少少成效，市民就會由怪責你變成怪責政府。<br />\n<br />\n「屌你老母阻住我返工」&rarr;「屌你老母政府唔回應市民訴求阻住大家發達」<br />\n<br />\n「屌你老母後生用暴力」&rarr;「屌你老母政府逼到大家用暴力」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">民意係欺善怕惡，只要大家堅持，爭取到成果，民意先會逆轉！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n民意並唔會因為你阻吓地鐵，出吓火攻就會逆轉！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港  時代革命 </span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"ab418d84dfe132ae75eb300b0614a9f1e77ae6f3","tid":1389793,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:49:17.000Z","msg":"光復香港　時代革命"},{"pid":"e45681264eab17e2da680d92eee2ec670ef1f54e","tid":1389793,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:49:27.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"b68428f0212eb0ee07b38258b33a824615b07ba0","tid":1389793,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:51:13.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"0338f17317439eba7e4891d114da84debfd24b29","tid":1389793,"uid":40335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:51:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5165f6fbada97ffa40c151ccd5fa751f0f0609a","tid":1389793,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:54:06.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"4b9c651ee49febbd98bd68f2d408cae54f289a57","tid":1389793,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:32:44.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"8dbba37bc49da4ea5fadbc7747f4f8187ce4311f","tid":1389793,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:33:02.000Z","msg":"光復開港  時代革命"},{"pid":"5b70bf9d78a3361a7f1ada6ddf96fb5fa8d86242","tid":1389793,"uid":260639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:17:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cab11dcc2792c07de5909dd150e7b74a8b210c11","tid":1389793,"uid":142433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:20:59.000Z","msg":"亨利中文幾好"},{"pid":"312240a100e7f3b5312d03f11e954966cecd025f","tid":1389793,"uid":121546,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:30:19.000Z","msg":"樓下d廢中成日傾政治，傾親都係鬧後生仔點點點，但依排我發覺有後生仔著全黑行過d廢中就會收哂聲，以前唔會，係武力升級左先係咁<br />\n廢中廢老都係欺善怕惡，武力愈升級，民意就愈唔敢反對你"},{"pid":"b21b94594c3e2f8789bd22435084e93df414d594","tid":1389793,"uid":128261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:19:48.000Z","msg":"亨利叫佢個黑警老婆打人果陣輕手啲啦"}]}